Tennis has brought her great wealth, particularly since Max Eisenbud, who helped to turn Maria Sharapova into the world's highest-earning sportswoman, became her agent. Since Eisenbud started signing up a host of sponsors keen to exploit the Chinese market, Li has jumped to second in the annual list of highest earners in women's sport compiled by Forbes magazine.
